According to an updated Alibaba prospectus on the U.S. Securities and Exchange Commission’s website, the number of active mobile users of the company’s services in July amounted to 188 million, significantly exceeding the March figure (163 million people).
At the same time, 32.8% of all Alibaba transactions in the past quarter were mobile devices.
